    {
      "instruction": "<p>Melt a generous knob of <strong>butter</strong> in a pot over a low heat</p><p>Once melted, remove the pot from the heat and add your <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>remaining rice vinegar</strong>,<strong> gochujang paste </strong>and<strong> sriracha</strong></p><p>Whisk until you have a thick sauce<strong> </strong>then season with<strong> pepper </strong>–<strong> </strong>this is your <strong>gochujang hollandaise</strong></p>",
