    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top a <strong>toasted ciabatta base</strong> with a few slices of <strong>tomato</strong>, a <strong>smashed sausage patty</strong>, a<strong> fried egg</strong>, a dollop of <strong>gochujang hollandaise </strong>and a <strong>ciabatta lid </strong>– this is your <strong>smashed sausage, fried egg & gochujang hollandaise sarnie</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>chips</strong>, <strong>sesame smashed cucumber</strong> and <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>gochujang hollandaise </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
